INCOSE GtWR Attributes that are equivalent to existing
SysML attributes are represented using derived properties.
Attribute names ending with an asterisk (*) are minimum
required to express a Need or Requirement.
Attribute multiplicity is defined as minimum 1 when the
attribute is required, causing the automatic UML
completeness validation suite to trigger a warning if the
Minimum required Attributes are used when computing the
